  | Respected shockumentary filmmaker RenΘ Wiesner, director of Mondo     |
  | Siam and the Pulp Films collection, is back! This time with a         |
  | documentary feature exploring the collection of a death enthusiast    |
  | and murderabilia collector opening his collection to the public for   |
  | the first time! Michael is a collector of true crime memorabilia and  |
  | murder art, with a unique archive unlike anything you have seen       |
